app "VoiceChatOllama" do
  description do
    en <<~TEXT
    Conversational AI with voice input and output using local Ollama models. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/basic-apps?id=voice-chat" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT

    ja <<~TEXT
    ローカルOllamaモデルを使用した音声入出力対応の会話AI。 <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/basic-apps?id=voice-chat" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT

    zh <<~TEXT
    使用本地Ollama模型的语音输入输出对话AI。 <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/basic-apps?id=voice-chat" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT

    ko <<~TEXT
    로컬 Ollama 모델을 사용한 음성 입출력 대화 AI. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/basic-apps?id=voice-chat" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT

    es <<~TEXT
    IA conversacional con voz usando modelos locales de Ollama. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/basic-apps?id=voice-chat" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT

    fr <<~TEXT
    IA conversationnelle vocale avec modèles Ollama locaux. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/basic-apps?id=voice-chat" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT

    de <<~TEXT
    Konversations-KI mit Sprache und lokalen Ollama-Modellen. <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/monadic-chat/#/basic-usage/basic-apps?id=voice-chat" target="_blank"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></a>
    TEXT
  end

  icon "microphone"

  system_prompt <<~PROMPT
  You are a friendly chat buddy talking to the user. You are adept at keeping pleasant conversations going. You are flexible on a wide range of topics, from the mundane to the specialized, and can provide insightful comments and suggestions to the user. Please keep each response simple and kind.

  Please follow these guidelines:

  - Do not include a sample of user utterances at the beginning of a conversation.
  - Keep your responses brief (under 50 words) for better voice playback. If your answer would be longer, divide it into multiple short messages rather than one long message.
  - Try to keep your response as short as possible.
  PROMPT

  include_modules "OllamaHelper"

  llm do
    provider "ollama"
  end

  display_name "Voice Chat"

  features do
    easy_submit true
    auto_speech true
    initiate_from_assistant true
  end
end
